<h1>We recently received a request to reset your password.</h1>
<p>To reset your password, click on the link below:</p>
<%= link_to "Reset my password",
						edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token,
																		email: @user.email) %>
<p>For your security, this link will expire in two hours.</p>
<p>If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this message and your password will remain the same.</p>